node.text: Using inspiration from the design and technology of the 2023 Cadillac LYRIQ, the LYRIQ Electriq Kitchen features a multisensory tasting menu that unites the rawness of nature with innovative artistry—created by chefs @NikiNakayama of @nnakarestaurant and Chef Jordan Kahn of @vespertine.la. #LYRIQ #LYRIQElectriqKitchen

node.title: LYRIQ Electriq Kitchen ft. Chef Jordan Kahn & Niki Nakayama

node.text: Using inspiration from the design and technology of the 2023 Cadillac LYRIQ, the LYRIQ Electriq Kitchen features a multisensory tasting menu that unites the rawness of nature with innovative artistry—created by chefs @NikiNakayama of @nnakarestaurant and Chef Jordan Kahn of @vespertine.la. #LYRIQ #LYRIQElectriqKitchen

node.text: Get to know @NikiNakayama, one of the chefs creating a tasting menu for the LYRIQ Electriq Kitchen inspired by the Cadillac LYRIQ. Not only is she the owner of @nnakarestaurant, an award-winning restaurant, but she was also featured on the first season of “Chef’s Table.” #LYRIQ #LYRIQElectriqKitchen
